title: ArtyTorrent Music Production Pack 2 - WAV Samples Loops 1 - Elab
description:
Welcome to my 2nd Music Production Pack

Elab XTcFiles of House Repack contains wave files, re-categorized, normalized, and trimmed appropriately. Many of the one-shots have been converted to mono to keep file size down. The original CD contained many "mixes" of the construction kits. I have removed these as they are pretty much useless to producers.

Any comments, questions or requests are welcome.
